---
// ExamplesSection — executable examples showcase
---

<section class="examples-showcase">
  <div class="container">
    <p class="section-label reveal">Executable Examples</p>
    <h2 class="section-title reveal">Executable examples when prose needs proof.</h2>
    <p class="section-sub reveal">
      Executable examples are one evidence source inside the same verification
      system. Use them for API flows, CLI sessions, and docs that need to stay exact.
    </p>

    <div class="examples-panels">
      <!-- Spec file with embedded example -->
      <div class="panel reveal" style="--reveal-delay: 0.1s">
        <div class="panel-bar">
          <div class="panel-dots"><span></span><span></span><span></span></div>
          <span class="panel-title">tasks/req/create.md</span>
        </div>
        <div class="panel-body code-panel">
          <pre><code><span class="c-muted">```http supersigil-ref=create-past-date</span>
<span class="c-teal">POST</span> <span class="c-text">/api/v1/tasks</span>
<span class="c-gray">Content-Type: application/json</span>

<span class="c-text">&#123;</span>
  <span class="c-teal">"title"</span><span class="c-gray">:</span> <span class="c-str">"Buy milk"</span><span class="c-gray">,</span>
  <span class="c-teal">"due_date"</span><span class="c-gray">:</span> <span class="c-str">"2020-01-01"</span>
<span class="c-text">&#125;</span>
<span class="c-muted">```</span>

<span class="c-muted">```supersigil-xml</span>
<span class="c-gold">&lt;Example</span>
  <span class="c-teal">id</span>=<span class="c-str">"create-past-date"</span>
  <span class="c-teal">runner</span>=<span class="c-str">"http"</span>
  <span class="c-teal">verifies</span>=<span class="c-str">"tasks/req/create#due-date"</span><span class="c-gold">&gt;</span>
  <span class="c-gold">&lt;Expected</span>
    <span class="c-teal">status</span>=<span class="c-str">"400"</span>
    <span class="c-teal">contains</span>=<span class="c-str">"due_date must be in the future"</span>
  <span class="c-gold">/&gt;</span>
<span class="c-gold">&lt;/Example&gt;</span>
<span class="c-muted">```</span></code></pre>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Terminal output -->
      <div class="panel reveal" style="--reveal-delay: 0.2s">
        <div class="panel-bar">
          <div class="panel-dots"><span></span><span></span><span></span></div>
          <span class="panel-title">Terminal</span>
        </div>
        <div class="panel-body term-panel">
          <pre><code><span class="c-muted">$</span> <span class="c-text">supersigil verify</span>

<b>&#8505;</b> Executing 3 examples:
  <span class="c-green"><b>&#10004;</b></span> tasks/req/create::create-task (http) <span class="c-green">passed</span>
  <span class="c-green"><b>&#10004;</b></span> tasks/req/create::create-missing-title (http) <span class="c-green">passed</span>
  <span class="c-red"><b>&#10006;</b></span> tasks/req/create::create-past-date (http) <span class="c-red">failed</span>
Examples: <b>2</b> passed, <span class="c-red"><b>1</b></span> failed
Failed examples:
  <span class="c-red"><b>&#10006;</b></span> <span class="c-teal">tasks/req/create::create-past-date</span> (http)
      [Status]
      expected: 400
      actual: 201</code></pre>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="examples-cta reveal" style="--reveal-delay: 0.35s">
      <a href="/supersigil/guides/executable-examples/" class="btn btn-ghost">
        See how examples fit into verification
        <svg viewBox="0 0 16 16" width="14" height="14" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M6 3l5 5-5 5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .examples-showcase {
    padding: 8rem 0;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .examples-panels {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 3rem;
  }
  .examples-cta {
    margin-top: 2rem;
    text-align: center;
  }
</style>
